03:49.730 --> 03:52.524
"My heart always timidly hides itself

03:52.608 --> 03:53.734
"behind my mind."

03:55.152 --> 03:57.487
"I set out to bring down stars

03:57.571 --> 03:58.822
"from the sky..."

03:59.615 --> 04:01.325
-"Ow. Ow.

04:01.408 --> 04:04.161
"Oh, my God,
four men are beating me.

04:04.244 --> 04:06.330
"My arm. I think it is broken.

04:06.413 --> 04:07.831
"Who are you guys?

04:07.915 --> 04:09.416
"Why? Why?

04:09.499 --> 04:12.836
"I'll give you anything
if you would only stop hitting me.

04:12.920 --> 04:14.838
"Please stop pulling my nose.

04:14.922 --> 04:16.298
"It is not fake.

04:16.381 --> 04:18.091
"I think I am dying.

04:18.175 --> 04:20.552
"Please take me to the hospital."

04:20.802 --> 04:22.679
Your words have bewitched me.

04:22.763 --> 04:24.556
I need your arms around me.

04:24.848 --> 04:26.308
Come to
my chamber at once.

04:26.391 --> 04:28.060
"Come to my chamber at once."

04:28.143 --> 04:31.313
- And bring pound cake.
-"And bring pound cake."

04:35.400 --> 04:36.652
Peter, please come to bed.

04:36.735 --> 04:38.320
Enough of the community watch.

04:38.403 --> 04:40.489
We live on a very safe street.

04:40.572 --> 04:43.075
Lois, you wouldn't believe
the things we see out there.

04:43.158 --> 04:46.078
There was a kid riding his bike
while holding a tennis racket.

04:46.161 --> 04:48.956
- For real.
- Come on! Let's fool around,

04:49.039 --> 04:50.374
or watch a movie,

04:50.457 --> 04:52.960
or finally click that
"Crackle" icon on the TV.

04:53.168 --> 04:55.546
Lois, I am an unelected vigilante,

04:55.629 --> 04:57.464
and I take my job very seriously.

04:57.548 --> 04:59.466
Like Serious George.

04:59.758 --> 05:01.343
Hey, George, want to go to the park?

05:01.426 --> 05:03.679
Thank you, but no.

05:03.762 --> 05:06.306
It's a beautiful day...
lots of mischief to get into.

05:06.390 --> 05:07.641
I don't doubt that,

05:07.724 --> 05:09.184
but as you can see,
I'm pretty busy.

05:09.268 --> 05:11.520
I'm trying to get
a head start on my taxes.

05:11.603 --> 05:14.147
Oh, I see... trying
to figure out a way

05:14.231 --> 05:15.774
to deduct <i>bananas?</i>

05:15.858 --> 05:18.902
'Cause I eat bananas. Terrific.

05:18.986 --> 05:21.196
Hey, your inside,
so don't wear a hat.

05:21.280 --> 05:24.491
Unless you're leaving,
which would be terrific also.

05:32.875 --> 05:34.793
What the hell? Hey, you!

05:36.753 --> 05:38.213
Step away from that table.

05:38.297 --> 05:41.717
Brain fart.
Window. Sorry.

05:42.593 --> 05:43.760
Hold it right there!

05:44.261 --> 05:46.263
I'm warning you!
Hands where I could see 'em.

05:56.523 --> 05:57.941
Cleveland Jr.?

05:58.108 --> 06:00.402
Mr. Griffin! You shot me!

06:00.611 --> 06:02.112
Oh, my God!

06:02.446 --> 06:04.406
Peter, where are you?

06:04.489 --> 06:08.744
Peter? Okay, I'm starting
<i>The Good Wife</i> without you.

06:08.827 --> 06:10.162
Phew! Heh.

06:10.245 --> 06:12.414
Unlike you, I just dodged a bullet.

06:19.421 --> 06:23.425
Okay, next is the... brown family.

06:23.509 --> 06:25.719
Oh. Oh, my goodness. I'm so sorry.

06:25.802 --> 06:27.930
Sometimes I write descriptions
of my patients

06:28.013 --> 06:29.223
to help me remember them.

06:29.306 --> 06:31.808
No, it's okay. Our last name is Brown.

06:31.892 --> 06:33.185
Oh, okay. Phew.

06:33.268 --> 06:35.979
Ah, then this must be
"Chubster Dumb-Dumb."

06:37.481 --> 06:39.191
I'm sorry, sir. No visitors.

06:39.274 --> 06:42.277
Excuse me, I'll have you know
I'm the shooter!

06:42.361 --> 06:43.779
So, how's he doing?

06:43.862 --> 06:46.031
"How's he doing"?
How do you think he's doing!

06:46.114 --> 06:47.491
You shot my son!

06:47.699 --> 06:49.243
Look, Cleveland, I'm real sorry.

06:49.326 --> 06:52.412
I thought someone was breaking
into your house, and I panicked.

06:52.496 --> 06:53.914
It was dark. I...

06:53.997 --> 06:55.457
I don't know
why he didn't just say it was him.

06:55.666 --> 06:58.252
I couldn't hear you.
I was listening to music,

06:58.335 --> 07:00.921
I went to turn it down,
and the next thing I know,

07:01.004 --> 07:02.005
you shot me!

07:02.089 --> 07:03.298
Why the hell
were you climbing in the window

07:03.382 --> 07:04.675
of your own house anyway?

07:04.842 --> 07:06.552
My dad says opening the door

07:06.635 --> 07:08.428
lets out too much air-conditioning.

07:08.554 --> 07:10.597
I already have a bullet in my son,

07:10.681 --> 07:12.349
I don't need one in my wallet.

07:12.432 --> 07:14.893
You wouldn't have fired
that gun if he was white!

07:14.977 --> 07:16.645
That's not true... I'll shoot anybody.

07:16.770 --> 07:17.855
Joe, give me your gun.

07:17.938 --> 07:19.398
Here you go... Hey, wait a second!

07:19.606 --> 07:21.358
Look, let's all just calm down.

07:21.525 --> 07:22.568
Calm down?

07:22.651 --> 07:24.611
I want this racist out the room,

07:24.695 --> 07:25.863
and I want him arrested!

07:25.988 --> 07:28.490
Racist? I put these gloves on
for everybody.

07:28.574 --> 07:29.867
Oh, oh, you're talking to him.

07:30.033 --> 07:33.161
Look, the police department
has deemed the shooting accidental.

07:33.245 --> 07:35.622
Given the circumstances,
Peter was within his rights

07:35.706 --> 07:36.748
to fire his weapon.

07:36.874 --> 07:39.918
And what about my son's rights
not to beshot?

07:40.127 --> 07:41.420
Look, Cleveland...

07:41.503 --> 07:43.547
Lat... Latisha?

07:43.755 --> 07:45.007
I thought he had a gun.

07:45.215 --> 07:47.801
I'd never want to do anything
to hurt you or your family.

07:47.885 --> 07:48.886
You're my friend.

07:49.052 --> 07:50.262
I was your friend.

07:50.345 --> 07:51.555
Now, get out of here!

07:51.638 --> 07:53.640
You're nothing but a worthless bigot!

07:56.852 --> 07:58.729
Wow, I really messed up.

07:58.812 --> 08:01.940
I haven't felt this bad
since I drove by that speed sign.

08:09.907 --> 08:11.408
Aw...

08:22.294 --> 08:24.421
Hey, does anybody know
if Cleveland's coming by?

08:24.505 --> 08:26.840
I was hoping to apologize
and collect his deposit

08:26.924 --> 08:29.384
- for the community watch shirts.
- I talked to him earlier.

08:29.468 --> 08:31.929
He... he doesn't want
to be anywhere near you.

08:32.095 --> 08:34.014
Hey, look, they're talking
about the shooting.

08:34.181 --> 08:35.516
Good evening. Two nights ago

08:35.599 --> 08:38.185
there was a shooting right here
in our own backyard.

08:38.268 --> 08:42.064
a 14-year-old boy
named Cleveland Brown Jr.

08:42.147 --> 08:44.525
Joining me tonight
is his father, Cleveland Brown.

08:44.608 --> 08:47.110
So that's not really Quahog?
It's just a big picture?

08:47.277 --> 08:49.780
Now, Mr. Brown, I understand
you're trying to get the police

08:49.863 --> 08:51.281
to reopen the investigation.

08:51.490 --> 08:53.867
That's right, Tom.
My family and I believe

08:53.951 --> 08:57.120
this shooting was a hate crime,
and we'd like to see Mr. Griffin

08:57.287 --> 08:59.081
held accountable for his actions.

08:59.248 --> 09:01.250
Hate crime? That's crazy!

09:01.333 --> 09:02.459
I love all people!

09:02.543 --> 09:04.127
I love blacks, I love Asians...

09:04.211 --> 09:06.463
hell, I even love gay Aborigines.

09:19.142 --> 09:21.228
Wow, this is just great, Peter.

09:21.311 --> 09:23.146
Everyone in town hates us now.

09:23.313 --> 09:25.858
The cashier at the grocery store
told her to "push on,"

09:25.941 --> 09:27.484
and then she snapped her fingers,

09:27.568 --> 09:30.571
and now I think she's my new
favorite lady in the world.

09:30.737 --> 09:33.282
I don't understand. I'm not a racist.

09:33.407 --> 09:35.701
It's well documented
that my dream three-way

09:35.784 --> 09:38.537
is S. Epatha Merkerson
and CCH Pounder.

09:38.745 --> 09:40.289
S., this is CCH.

09:40.372 --> 09:41.832
CCH, this is S.

09:41.915 --> 09:43.667
It is my intention that we conduct this

09:43.750 --> 09:45.836
with both sexiness and dignity.

09:46.128 --> 09:47.838
Peter, this is a hot-button issue.

09:47.921 --> 09:50.507
I mean, you shot
an African-American kid.

09:50.591 --> 09:52.176
Of course this isn't just gonna go away.

09:52.342 --> 09:54.761
Well, there's got to be something I can do
to make things right.

09:54.928 --> 09:57.472
I'll just have to prove to everybody
that I'm not a racist.

09:57.556 --> 09:59.725
- How are you gonna do that?
- Well, for starters,

09:59.808 --> 10:01.518
I'm gonna head over to the YMCA.

10:01.602 --> 10:03.395
There's nothing black guys like more

10:03.478 --> 10:06.440
than out-of-shape
indoor-basketball white guys.

10:08.192 --> 10:11.069
Hey! I'm trying my best here.

10:11.153 --> 10:13.530
And trying is what matters most of all.

10:13.947 --> 10:14.990
You're right, Peter.

10:15.073 --> 10:16.533
We need to give you a chance,

10:16.617 --> 10:18.285
no matter what color your skin is.

10:18.368 --> 10:20.037
Come on, let's play some ball.

10:21.705 --> 10:25.125
"...and then Peter and his new friends
went for ice cream."

10:25.209 --> 10:26.460
The end.

10:27.961 --> 10:30.547
Okay, kids, are your parents
out of the room?

10:30.631 --> 10:34.468
Good. Let's get back
to <i>Sloppy Floppers</i> magazine.

10:39.723 --> 10:40.891
What are you doing?

10:40.974 --> 10:43.060
Lois, to show I'm in touch
with what it's like

10:43.143 --> 10:45.354
to be African-American,
I am gonna go to the middle

10:45.437 --> 10:48.440
of the town square, get naked
and paint myself brown.

10:48.524 --> 10:50.400
No, no, that's offensive.

10:50.484 --> 10:51.818
You can't pretend to be black.

10:51.902 --> 10:53.237
That's a stupid idea.

10:53.320 --> 10:55.280
- What?
-It's a stupid idea!

10:55.364 --> 10:58.825
You're a stupid man!
A stupid, stupid man!

10:58.909 --> 11:01.912
Ow, you're hurting me!
Stop it, stop it, Lois!

11:01.995 --> 11:04.414
No! I'm so sick of your crap.

11:04.498 --> 11:06.792
