them to me before you do them?

11:10.295 --> 11:12.714
Are you trying to get a rise out of me?

11:12.798 --> 11:16.176
Are you happy now?
Is this what you want?

11:16.260 --> 11:18.220
Oh, no, it's not what I want!

11:18.303 --> 11:21.223
It's not what I want.
I'm sorry, I'm sorry.

11:22.850 --> 11:25.686
It's never been this bad before.
What do we do?

11:25.769 --> 11:27.312
What we always do.

11:27.771 --> 11:30.899
I'm in charge of my head...
that much I know!

11:36.822 --> 11:39.157
What the hell
are you doing on my property?

11:39.241 --> 11:40.951
Look, it's time we bury the hatchet.

11:41.034 --> 11:42.828
So I brought a bottle
of your favorite booze.

11:42.911 --> 11:45.080
Now let's just have a drink
and put this all behind us.

11:45.163 --> 11:46.748
I don't want nothing from you.

11:46.832 --> 11:48.208
Well, hold on, I got something else.

11:48.458 --> 11:50.961
Cigars. We can smoke 'em together,
all happy,

11:51.044 --> 11:52.963
like a bunch of douche bags
outside a wedding.

11:53.088 --> 11:54.214
Peter, get out of here.

11:54.298 --> 11:56.508
I'm never gonna forgive you
for what you did.

11:56.675 --> 11:58.677
Aw, come on.
This'll change your mind.

12:01.680 --> 12:03.891
Oh, my God!
Quick, do something!

12:06.560 --> 12:08.562
It's not working. Get rid of it!

12:15.694 --> 12:17.446
Get your family out of that house!

12:17.529 --> 12:19.239
If they don't leave, they'll die.

12:19.323 --> 12:21.116
Round up your family and get out

12:21.200 --> 12:22.326
or you're all gonna be sorry.

12:22.409 --> 12:23.702
Get out, now!

12:25.037 --> 12:27.164
See, kids, I told you
we'd make friends here.

12:27.247 --> 12:30.292
I guess me getting transferred
by the Xerox Corporation

12:30.375 --> 12:32.252
wasn't the worst thing
after all.

12:41.303 --> 12:42.638
Oh, thank God, Joe.

12:42.721 --> 12:44.723
Are you here to give me
the deposit for the shirts?

12:44.932 --> 12:46.808
No, Peter, I'm here to place you
under arrest

12:46.892 --> 12:48.936
for the attempted murder
of Cleveland Jr.

12:49.102 --> 12:51.480
What are you talkin' about?
You know it was an accident.

12:51.563 --> 12:54.233
Yeah, but let's just say,
public opinion has shifted.

12:54.316 --> 12:56.860
And the boys upstairs said
they can no longer ignore it.

12:56.944 --> 12:58.695
