fall in love with me.

13:39.987 --> 13:42.364
Then... we'll see what happens.

13:42.447 --> 13:45.576
Oh, no. It's already working.

13:45.826 --> 13:47.703
Griffin, you have a visitor.

13:48.579 --> 13:51.331
- Carter? What are you doing here?
- Hello, Griffin.

13:51.415 --> 13:53.250
I'd like to talk to you
about these charges

13:53.333 --> 13:54.751
that have been
brought against you.

13:54.835 --> 13:56.670
Why don't we go somewhere
a little more private?

13:57.379 --> 13:59.965
I... guess I'll see you in a little bit?

14:00.048 --> 14:02.134
